{"tid":1001604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 陳帆：紅磡站北面連接隧道、列車停放處、南面連接隧道同樣出現問題","createTime":"2019-01-30T09:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T12:16:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f281e893eb7d1c8cea16b1d774648eb7ef94433d","tid":1001604,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2385664/org/1da8249cf2f667f29e572b613fb9ce03.jpg/jHW3fZG0MvbfzHgQquVXCsn-T2FPrAqA-qI2rfqiNq0?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2385664%2Forg%2F1da8249cf2f667f29e572b613fb9ce03.jpg%2FjHW3fZG0MvbfzHgQquVXCsn-T2FPrAqA-qI2rfqiNq0%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=f4c27fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局局長陳帆、路政署署長陳派明和屋宇署署長張天祥，今日（30日）下午4點舉行記者會。陳帆表示紅磡站除了已公布的問題外，北面連接隧道、列車停放處、南面連接隧道同樣出現問題，施工紀錄缺失，未經同意改動，其中紀錄缺失達四成之多，但政府現時掌握資料有限。<br />\n陳帆確認，沙中線開通一定受到影響，說不清沙中線可以何時開通。<br />\n港鐵代表將於下午5時半見傳媒，料將就工程問題回應政府說法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/289561/沙中線再出事-陳帆-紅磡站另三處缺施工紀錄擅改圖則-開通受阻\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F289561%2F%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%B7%9A%E5%86%8D%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%8B-%E9%99%B3%E5%B8%86-%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1%E7%AB%99%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%89%E8%99%95%E7%BC%BA%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E6%93%85%E6%94%B9%E5%9C%96%E5%89%87-%E9%96%8B%E9%80%9A%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BB&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=32850961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/289561/沙中線再出事-陳帆-紅磡站另三處缺施工紀錄擅改圖則-開通受阻</a>"},{"pid":"801c5ea767df9c500a3b2fb3780dc92c6cc26e1e","tid":1001604,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:22:26.000Z","msg":"成條線重建不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc231519d7fa0e34db423e8c86620d6b42aaf86","tid":1001604,"uid":53122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"801c5ea767d